6. How do electric needle-free injectors work?
Electric needle-free injectors use high-pressure technology to inject medication through the skin without a needle.

7. Are electric needle-free injectors safe for home use?
Yes, electric needle-free injectors are designed for ease of use and are considered safe for self-administration at home.

